{"tid":2047394,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利物浦單膝跪的偽善","createTime":"2020-06-02T05:29:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T07:35:45.000Z","uid":33775,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"31644bd7bb4ecc2045af945ce4e0eae949c62395","tid":2047394,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:29:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2020/06/02/207180/利物浦單膝跪george-floyd-的偽善\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2020%2F06%2F02%2F207180%2F%E5%88%A9%E7%89%A9%E6%B5%A6%E5%96%AE%E8%86%9D%E8%B7%AAgeorge-floyd-%E7%9A%84%E5%81%BD%E5%96%84&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbfo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=110003c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2020/06/02/207180/利物浦單膝跪george-floyd-的偽善</a><br />\n<br />\n今日新聞報導英超著名頂班球隊利物浦為對逝世美國非裔人士George Floyd 致悼念，在其球場Anfield，其球員以單膝下跪以悼念George Floyd並表示反對美國警暴。<br />\n<br />\n相信唔少西方左翼份子以及反法西斯份子會表示「個畫面好靚呀！」<br />\n<br />\n但自問見到係「見到一個偽善的行為。」<br />\n<br />\n悼念George Floyd，以表示反對美國警暴，我明，甚至支持，但唔該做就做全套，做就做得有條理，如果係講警暴，想講香港三個星期前一樣出現有位南亞裔人士被警壓頸後不治，但點解無人出來鬧警暴？身為前宗主國，有冇出過一句聲？英國有不少南亞裔人士，點解利物浦唔出句聲既？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XBjHqSM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXBjHqSM.jpg&h=d21f7d79&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28cfc664d62875e0a6430fa84ea5e358ba9cb3a2","tid":2047394,"uid":249041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:30:36.000Z","msg":"猁狗"},{"pid":"08a7bbde7b3ae829fb4849d8981ac1cd20d270dd","tid":2047394,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:32:09.000Z","msg":"大家都係警暴, 但人仔要奶所以冇野講"},{"pid":"59f5b0a111b3b3b4908dd2ec3ab008f1c7da18fb","tid":2047394,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:33:21.000Z","msg":"唔過2頁"},{"pid":"c1a03e903f95c0c14910c1bb52bdeda06c4d9963","tid":2047394,"uid":11849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:3